<div class="title">I Love Amphetamine</div>
<div class="substance">Amphetamines (Adderall)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=speed+freak&Exact=1">speed freak</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; speed freak. "I Love Amphetamine: An Experience with Amphetamines (Adderall) (exp8639)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jul 1, 2005. erowid.org/exp/8639</div>

<br/>



